‘My daughter came out and said “we made you something”. The next minute Scott came out with three cards saying “welcome home mummy” to cover it up,’ Caitlin recalled.

What the touching video doesn’t show is Caitlin’s shocked reaction as Scott handed her a ring just as their daughters held up the ‘marry daddy?’ card.

‘I was sitting on the couch in the lounge room and he was sitting next to me and pulled the ring out,’ Caitlin said.

‘He was shaking I was shaking and crying and flicked the ring across the room. Meanwhile, my oldest daughter was sick at the time and lying down. It was just typical us as parents,’ she laughed.

